data.description: Fantastic Location on Fairview Plaza with back wallkway to Pennsylvania and Glenridge.  The grand sitting room, with its high ceiling and classic charm, sets the tone for the rest of the house. This is a once in a lifetime opportunity to restore a forever home in the historic Almond Grove neighborhood of Los Gatos. The formal living room and dining room, both boasting high ceilings and large windows, are flooded with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. Kitchen opens up to a private balcony and deck, offering picturesque views.  Bonus 527 sf attic space plus 591 sf of basement and 170 sf of storage ready to buildout!  Charming sunny yard, with steps down to Pennsylvania Ave. Located just blocks away from downtown Los Gatos, you'll have access to award-winning restaurants, Bachman Park, Los Gatos Schools, and beautiful hiking and biking trails. Don't miss out on the chance to own a piece of history in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in Los Gatos.
